Lower Super Output Level (LSOA) metadata for...
JSON file containing metadata at Lower Layer Super Output Area (LSOA).
Super Output Areas are a geographic hierarchy designed to improve the reporting of small-area statistics.
In the 2021 Census there were 35,672 LSOAs in England and Wales.
LSOAs are built from contiguous Output Areas.
